<HEADLINE> Chinese Ambassador to France Hosts Reception </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, September 30 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Ambassador to France Wu
Jianmin hosted a reception at the Chinese embassy here Thursday
evening to celebrate the 50th anniversary of the founding of the
People's Republic of China.
</P>
<P>
French Interior Minister Jean-Pierre Chevenement, former Prime
Minister Edouard Balladur and 1,000 other French and Chinese
guests attended the reception.
</P>
<P>
Chevenement told Wu that the founding day of the People's
Republic of China is an important date and China has made
tremendous achievements in the past 50 years. 
