<HEADLINE> Karl Marx Voted Thinker of Millennium </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, October 1 (Xinhua) -- Karl Marx was voted the thinker
of the millennium in a poll conducted by BBC's News On-line
Service and the result was published on Friday.
</P>
<P>
The father of communism just pipped scientists Albert Einstein
and Isaac Newton in the poll.
</P>
<P>
In earlier on-line polls, William Shakespeare was picked as the
greatest writer of the last 1,000 years and former beetle Sir Paul
McCartney was chosen as the greatest composer. 
</P>
</TEXT>
