<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 1 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major
world cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on October 2, issued by
China's Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 9 degrees C., max. 20 degrees C., cloudy to clear,
moderate to strong breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 21 degrees C., max. 27 degrees C., overcast, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Bangkok: min. 24 degrees C., max. 31 degrees C., thunder
showers to cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
