<P>
ALMA-ATA, October 1 (Xinhua) -- Kazakh President Nursultan
Nazarbayev on Saturday accepted Prime Minister Nurlan Utebovich
Balgimbaev's resignation and appointed Deputy Prime Minister and
Minister of Foreign Affairs Kasymzhomart Tokayev as the acting
prime minister.
</P>
<P>
