boulevard.
</P>
<P>
They are followed by formations of army vehicles and missiles.
</P>
<P>
Conspicuous in the tank processions is a new type of tanks
designed and manufactured in China. It is light in weight, thick
in armor and strong in firepower.
</P>
<P>
The tank can attack targets both in the day and at night.
</P>
<P>
The new type is expected to become the main battle tank of the
Chinese armed forces, military sources say. 
