present a slogan of "Long Live the Motherland" and a huge national
flag of the People's Republic of China.
</P>
<P>
The parade will feature 38 formations with 90 floats, a great
number of models, sculptures and banners illustrating new China's
achievements over the past five decades. Traditional Chinese
dragon and lion dances will also be performed during the parade.
</P>
<P>
The 50-minute parade covers three themes on "Founding of new
China", "Reform and opening" and "Marching into the new century".
