<P>
-- Tian'anmen Rostrum takes on a new look after completion of a
facelift and is part of the venue for the grand celebration of the
50th anniversary of the founding of People's Republic of China.
</P>
<P>
-- About 500,000 people, including armymen and civilians,
gathered at the Tian'anmen Square and adjacent streets to
celebrate the 50th anniversary of the birth of PRC. 
</P>
</TEXT>
